data.description: Sellers have an assumable VA loan at 3.25% interest rate!! Welcome Home! Rare Ranch model sitting on large 0.26 acre lot in a lovely cul-de-sac with no neighbors behind! Open floorplan features 4 bedrooms, 3 baths & partially finished basement. Updated kitchen has granite counters & tile backsplash, newer stainless steel appliances (New dishwasher!) & laminate hardwood flooring. Opens to spacious family room with vaulted ceiling & fireplace. Second living area could be formal dining or living room. Sizeable Primary Suite has large wall closet with dual doors & attached, updated 4-pc bath. Two secondary bedrooms located near full hall bath. Outside find a large yard with many large trees, patio with gazebo cover & storage shed – plenty of space for boat/RV parking! The full basement contains the 4th bedroom & updated 3/4 bath along with an unfinished portion perfect for storage or to finish as you wish! Laundry room incudes washer & dryer. Many storage closets throughout & attached 2 car garage offers more storage. Solar panels for low utility bills! No HOA! Feeds to Cherry Creek School District! Just minutes to park, public transit, shopping & dining. Easy access to E470, I225, CC Reservoir, DTC & DIA. 14-mo Home Buyer’s Warranty Included.
